<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="7Jul1931"><font color="red">7 July 1931</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I have spoken with Eliot and am agreeing to accept the written offer his firm has just made to acquire the rights of <i>Work in Progress</i> for &pound;150 down on signing the contract. Terms 15%. </div>
